extendedInfo.description: Favorite hunting animal calls.Cougar, crocodile, crow, deer, duck, elephant, elk, fox, goose, grouse, moose, owl, rabbit, rattlesnake, seal, and wolf.Press to play, long press to install as a ringtone/notification/alarm and set as a ringtone.1.4 Updates:- multi-language (please help with translations if they are wrong)1.3.1 Updates:- app 2 SD for Froyo
